Text: This undertaking took far more patience and sanity than I'll ever have, and for that, I tip my hat to you. Thank you a ton!

I SALUTE YOU SIR ! While I don't claim to understand the intricacies and chord structures, etc , I just love the feel and sound of Flamenco. I have some of the Paco de Lucia albums but this undertaking truly speaks of your magnificent passion !
